Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.05,0:00:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up — I'm Carlos. I've built and\Npromoted businesses across the U.S. and\Nglobally.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.96,0:00:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Today I'll show you, step by step, how Pzhisen —\Npzhisen.online — makes promotion ridiculously\Nfast and fully automated.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.95,0:00:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Getting started is incredibly simple,\Nfast, and convenient.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.17,0:00:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You open the site, share your business idea, and\Ndeploy your AI employee team in minutes — no\Ncomplicated setup, no credit card required to\Nbegin.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.97,0:00:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Once your agents are live, they work for you\Ntwenty-four hours a day, seven days a week,\Nthree hundred sixty-five days a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.37,0:00:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,They never sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.55,0:00:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,They never take a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.11,0:00:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,They never clock out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.47,0:01:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,With Pzhisen, specialized AI agents\Nautomatically create promotional marketing\Ntweets and social copy for your brand.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.07,0:01:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,They produce promotional marketing\Nvideos ready for distribution.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.05,0:01:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,They write promotional marketing emails\Nand send them to mainstream inboxes\Nworldwide — Gmail, Outlook, and more.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.40,0:01:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,They automatically reply to customer\Nservice messages, so your clients always\Nget help — day or night.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.70,0:01:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,They automatically analyze your market\Ncompetitiveness, your sales data, and\Nreal-time market conditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.73,0:01:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,They research industry trends and help\Nyou understand where the world's major\Nsectors are heading next.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.83,0:01:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Then they publish for you across the world's\Nbiggest platforms: YouTube, TikTok, X, Facebook,\NWeChat Channels, Douyin, Tencent Video,\NKuaishou, Xiaohongshu — and more.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.29,0:02:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether you have a personal website or a full\Nenterprise site, Pzhisen helps anyone, anywhere,\Npromote and grow online — fully automated.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.11,0:02:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And here's the result that matters most: Pzhisen has\Nalready helped thousands of individuals and businesses\Nworldwide generate one million dollars in revenue in a\Nsingle month through AI-powered promotion and marketing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.12,0:02:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're ready to put an AI team to\Nwork while you sleep, go to\Npzhisen.online — and start tonight.
